    title: "Navigating Miami's Water: A Look at Watermakers' Approach to Purity",
    excerpt: "Miami, a city synonymous with sun and vibrant life, also faces a unique set of challenges when it comes to its tap water. Sourced primarily from the vast **Biscayne Aquifer**, the water making its way to homes and businesses often carries tell-tale signs of its journey: elevated levels of chlorin...",
